OL,3,CDefendant changes plea in murder trial
OL,4,Cafter woman shot dead
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to the murder
OL,7,Fof a woman shot dead in Talbot Green
OL,8,Fearlier this year.
OL,10,FMarcus Huntley, who's 21, had denied
OL,11,Fmurder, but changed his plea at
OL,12,FCardiff Crown Court.
OL,14,FHuntley was on trial alongside five
OL,15,Fother defendants following the
OL,16,Fincident in Rhondda Cynon Taf.
OL,18,FYesterday a jury heard Huntley had
OL,19,Ffired the shot that killed Joanne
OL,20,FPenney on March 9th, after Ms Penney
OL,21,Fopened the door at 10 Llys Illtyd.
