OL,6,FProsecutor Jonathan Rees KC said
OL,7,FHuntley "leant forward and immediately
OL,8,Fshot at the person who opened the
OL,9,Fdoor" after a fellow defendant knocked.
OL,11,FThe jury heard the killing had taken
OL,12,Fplace against the background of "the
OL,13,Fclash of two organised crime groups."
OL,15,FIt's claimed the "Rico" group wanted
OL,16,Fto "show its strength" to a rival
OL,17,Fcrime gang, after suffering two
OL,18,F"humiliations" in the preceding weeks.
