OL,3,CDefendant changes plea in murder trial
OL,4,Cafter woman shot dead
OL,6,FJoshua Gordon, 27; Melissa Quailey-
OL,7,FDashper, 40; Kristina Ginova, 21; and
OL,8,FTony Porter, 68, all from
OL,9,FLeicestershire, deny murder and
OL,10,Fparticipation in the activities of an
OL,11,Forganised crime group.
OL,13,FJordan Mills-Smith, 33, from Cardiff,
OL,14,Fdenies murder.
OL,16,FMills-Smith and Huntley had previously
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to participation in the
OL,18,Factivities of an organised crime group.
