OL,6,FAfter instructing the the jury to
OL,7,Fformally return a guilty verdict
OL,8,Fagainst Marcus Huntley, Mr Justice
OL,9,FFordham told the defendant:
OL,11,F"You have been convicted by the jury
OL,12,Fof murder on the basis of your plea
OL,13,Ftoday of guilty."
OL,15,F"You will be remanded in custody
OL,16,Fpending sentence in this court."
OL,18,F"I'm not making a decision about when
OL,19,Fsentence will take place but it will
OL,20,Fbe certainly after proceedings have
OL,21,Fended in this case."
